snippet.title: ADACA Release Teaser
snippet.description:
ADACA is set to release on Steam July 2022!

Wishlist it now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1765780/ADACA/?beta=0

Support this game: https://siris-pendrake.itch.io/adaca

ADACA is a Sci-fi First-person shooter set on the mysterious titular planet. Use your gravity-manipulating robotic arm to hurl heavy objects at your foes or even rip their weapons directly from their hands! Explore and manipulate the environment to stay alive and navigate this eerie, hostile world!


Follow The Development of ADACA: 
My Twitter: https://twitter.com/SirisTheDragon
Devlog: https://siris-pendrake.itch.io/adaca/...
Or subscribe to this channel!
